## 6. Scene Context Format

The add-on can optionally prepend a JSON scene description to every prompt:

```json
{
  "scene_name": "Scene",
  "frame_current": 1,
  "active_object": "Cube",
  "selected": ["Cube"],
  "objects": [
    {
      "name": "Cube",
      "type": "MESH",
      "location": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0],
      "mesh": { "vertices": 8, "polygons": 6, "materials": ["Material"] }
    }
  ]
}
```

This lets the AI reference existing objects by name and avoid conflicts.

