## 9. Extending the Add-on

### Add a new AI provider

1. Add an entry to `preferences.py` → `ai_provider` EnumProperty items.
2. Add a `_call_<provider>` method in `utils/ai_client.py`.
3. Handle it in `AIClient.chat()`.

### Streaming responses

Use `requests` with `stream=True` and call `bpy.app.timers.register` on each
chunk to update `context.scene.ai_response_display` incrementally.

### File import (OBJ / FBX / GLTF)

Have the AI return `{"action": "import_file", "url": "...", "format": "gltf"}`
and handle it in a dedicated operator that uses `bpy.ops.import_scene.*`.

### Geometry Nodes graph generation

Ask the AI to return node graph descriptions as JSON, then translate each node
type to `nodes.new(type_string)` calls.  See `assets/example_prompts.py` for
a working scatter example.
